            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Gaiprandus"
                                >Gaiprand</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">vir devotus</rs>
                        <foreign>si indirizza alla </foreign><rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/254">beati sancti
                            Frigidiani</orgName> loco <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/750"
                            >Griciano</placeName>. <foreign>Gaiprando</foreign> quia in <rs
                            key="#Army">exercito</rs> ad <placeName>Francia</placeName> iteratus sum
                        ambulandum, proinde consideratus sum Dei temure et mercide anime me qualiter
                        aliquid de <rs key="#Landed_possessions">rebus</rs> meis pro anima mea
                        Dominus offerat, qualiter mihi Dominus pro parba tribuit magna <foreign>etc.
                            Perciò offre</foreign> Deo et tibi ecclesie beati Sancti Frigidiani et
                            <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> qui inibi ordinatus est aut in antea
                        fueret <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> ubi <persName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"><name ref="Fileradus"
                            >Filerat</name></persName> massario resedet, hic in <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Acorns"
                            ref="#places/750">Griciano</placeName>, una cum <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >terra</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">oliveto</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Acorns">silva</rs>, cultum et incultum, mobile et inmobile,
                        omnia et in omnibus, quantum modo ad ipsa casa pertenet, excepto duas <rs
                            key="#Petiae">petzas</rs> de terra ad <placeName key="#Petiae"
                            ref="#places/750">deblo <persName><name ref="Iustulus"
                                >Iustuli</name></persName>,</placeName> quod in meo reserbo
                        potestatem. <foreign>La donazione è finalizzata alle preghiere per la sua
                            anima e alla luminaria. Se ne riserva la potestas finché sia in vita.
                            Pena: maledizione e</foreign> soledos duocentum.
                            <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer"><name
                                ref="Sigebertus">Sichipert</name></persName> amico meo. (…) Actum in
                            <placeName ref="#places/750">Griciano</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Gaiprand viri devoti aucturi; +
                            <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Rotcaido"
                                >Rotcaido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> germano eius testis; +
                            <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name
                                ref="Gausbertus">Gauspert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> similiter germano eius
                        testis; + <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohanni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis.
                            <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: Sichipert </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
